{"data": [{"id": "4740936", "title": "Politics And The Markets 12/06/24", "description": "<p><span>This is the forum for daily political discussion on Seeking Alpha. A new version is published every market day.</span></p> <p>Please don't leave political comments on other articles or posts on the site.</p> <p>The comments below are not regulated with the same rigor as the rest of the site, and this is an <strong>'enter at your own risk' </strong>area as discussion can get very heated. If you can't stand the heat... you know what they say...</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>More on Today's Markets:</span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Moderation Guidelines:</b></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><span></span></b>We remove comments under the following categories:</p> <ul> <li>Personal attacks on another user account</li> <li>Anti-Vaxxer or covid related misinformation</li> <li>Stereotyping, prejudiced or racist language about individuals or the topic under discussion.</li> <li>Inciting violence messages, encouraging hate groups and political violence.</li> </ul> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regardless of which side of the political divide you find yourself, please be courteous and don't direct abuse at other users.</p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">For any issue with regards to comments please email us at : moderation@seekingalpha.com.</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Seeking Alpha's Disclosure:</span></b><span> Past performance is no guarantee of future results. No recommendation or advice is being given as to whether any investment is suitable for a particular investor. Any views or opinions expressed above may not reflect those of Seeking Alpha as a whole. Seeking Alpha is not a licensed securities dealer, broker or US investment adviser or investment bank. Our analysts are third party authors that include both professional investors and individual investors who may not be licensed or certified by any institute or regulatory body.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"> </p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <div class=\"sa-art article-width paywall-full-content\" id=\"a-body\"><span class=\"content-end p p1\"></span></div>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740936-politics-and-the-markets-120624", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 08:00:00"}, {"id": "4742522", "title": "SVIX: All Quiet On The Western Front", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A group of pens and pencils arranged as a graph\" data-id=\"2159569962\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>Akin the namesake movie, volatility can take sudden turns with the advent of an economic or political event. The introduction of ETFs catered towards this asset class has allowed investors to take a view on market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159569962/image_2159569962.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742522-svix-etf-sell-given-current-vix-levels", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 07:55:42"}, {"id": "4742519", "title": "Employers Holdings Has Room To Grow", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Finance background\" data-id=\"625756386\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">honglouwawa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Employers Holdings, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EIG\" title=\"Employers Holdings, Inc.\">EIG</a></span>) has emerged stronger than ever from the pandemic era. The firm boasts record profitability, with its core business benefitting from a reduction in the rate of adverse expenses and losses due to workers compensation. This is likely</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/625756386/image_625756386.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742519-employers-holdings-stock-attractively-valued-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 07:35:57"}, {"id": "4742518", "title": "DTCR: Data Centers And Digital Infrastructure For AI Exposure", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"IT technician fixing an outage on a network server\" data-id=\"1346929921\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"958px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Two years after the launch of ChatGPT by OpenAI, the artificial intelligence theme continues to make headlines, and for those still wondering whether it is still time to invest, it depends on the area of the AI ecosystem being targeted, one of which</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346929921/image_1346929921.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742518-dtcr-etf-data-centers-digital-infrastructure-for-ai-exposure", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 07:28:10"}, {"id": "4742517", "title": "Dollarama Q3: The Veneer Loses Some Of Its Shine, Management Comments Offer Hints", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar sign blowing away\" data-id=\"1142952057\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"9452px\" height=\"5289px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">pick-uppath</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>(All financial data is in Canadian dollars unless otherwise stated)</em></p> <p>Dollarama (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DOL:CA\" title=\"Dollarama Inc.\">DOL:CA</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DLMAF\" title=\"Dollarama Inc.\">OTCPK:DLMAF</a>), Canada's not-quite equivalent chain of low-priced everyday items when compared against U.S. giants Dollar Tree (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DLTR\" title=\"Dollar Tree, Inc.\">DLTR</a>) and Dollar General (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742517-dollarama-q3-the-veneer-loses-some-of-its-shine-management-comments-offer-hints", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 07:07:30"}, {"id": "4742515", "title": "Capital Southwest: Buying The Dip Despite Dividend Risks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Excited Businessman Raises Hands and Punches Air while Celebrating Successful Deal. Stock Exchange Manager Happy After Investment Day. Broker in White Shirt Wins a Profitable Contract. Back View\" data-id=\"2045262949\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">gorodenkoff</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Capital Southwest (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CSWC\" title=\"Capital Southwest\">CSWC</a></span>) has provided investors with quite a lot of volatility over the last six months, when its stock price has decreased by over 10%. Lower valuation combined with an attractive dividend yield leaves investors wondering whether the recent</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742515-capital-southwest-stock-buying-dip-despite-dividend-risks", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 06:59:04"}, {"id": "4742514", "title": "IWF May Struggle To Sustain Its Robust Return In 2025, But IWD Could Shine", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Year 2025 business concept. Economic and financial analysis, interest rates, stocks, bonds, ranking, mortgage, loan rates, Percent, up or down, arrow symbol, copy space. navy blue background\" data-id=\"2173998931\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Andrzej Rostek</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The solid tech earnings, rate cuts and economic growth continue to offer a cushion against lofty valuation, helping iShares Russell 1000 Growth ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IWF\" title=\"iShares Russell 1000 Growth ETF\">IWF</a></span>) soar to its all-time high. Although these factors are likely to favour the stock</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742514-iwf-may-struggle-sustain-robust-return-2025-but-iwd-could-shine", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 06:50:15"}, {"id": "4742512", "title": "SPYI: A 12% Yield With A Nice Tax Treatment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two executive businessperson colleagues consultation\" data-id=\"1809155192\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">bymuratdeniz</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The NEOS S&amp;P 500 High Income ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">BATS:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPYI\" title=\"Neos S&amp;P 500(R) High Income ETF\">SPYI</a></span>) has become a niche favorite in the income investing world since its launch in August 2022, and now has a considerable AUM, now exceeding $2B.</p> <p></p> <p>This isn't as large as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742512-spyi-a-12-percent-yield-with-a-nice-tax-treatment", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 06:15:31"}, {"id": "4742510", "title": "Super Micro Computer: A Lesson In Falling Knives", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Matching knife on the banks of the taiga river. Accessories for hike.\" data-id=\"1340511224\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Evgenyi Filatov/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I originally covered Super Micro Computer (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4719242-super-micro-a-lesson-in-big-multiples\">in early September</a>. At the time, the stock had experienced a 20% drop from the release of a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4144132-super-micro-drops-after-new-short-report-from-hindenburg-research\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noopener\">report</a> by Hindenburg Research.</p> <p></p> <p>Priced around $55 when the report came</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1340511224/image_1340511224.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742510-super-micro-computer-stock-stay-watchful-maintain-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 06:04:10"}, {"id": "4742516", "title": "Samsara Inc. 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Samsara Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106056\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742516-samsara-inc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 05:59:23"}]}